---
title: 'Chocka' Beef Burger & Fries with Charred Pineapple, Fried Egg & Burger Sauce
description: We know some people have mixed feelings about pineapple on pizza, but how about on a burger? We argue that it gives this beef
burger that extra fresh edge. If that hasn’t quipped your interest, what about adding an egg because everyone loves an egg. Trust
us, you’ll be team pineapple all the way!
